span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/pedrojg\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/975128b879696bf912c9cf06e2d52bab?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/975128b879696bf912c9cf06e2d52bab?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/pedrojg\" class=\"reviewer-name\">pedrojg</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">October 3, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Muy intuitivo para agregar muchas opciones, al principio parece un poco dificil por que todo es con codigo pero ya despues que le encuentras el modo te das cuenta que es de gran ayuda.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Pesimo</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/rodrigotorres\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8b585ce97ef14dbf72c6e035b2924571?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8b585ce97ef14dbf72c6e035b2924571?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/rodrigotorres\" class=\"reviewer-name\">rodrigotorres</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">September 28, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Se actualiza y arruina todo lo hecho en el sitio</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Poor Support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/briannie\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8d9c47347771152bef5ec4bb77bf3c0f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8d9c47347771152bef5ec4bb77bf3c0f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/briannie\" class=\"reviewer-name\">briannie</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">September 21, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I often see reviews that are one star and the author complains that the reviewer never raised a support question before giving one star.  Well, I raised a question, received a standard answer which did not address my query and despite asking again a number of times the author ignores me.\n\nThis is a popular plugin and it works well but clearly the support has failed to meet my hopes.  I know authors are not obliged to give help or assistance but it would be nice and won\'t encourage me to go Pro or indeed buy anything that this author promotes.</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:13:\"download_link\";s:63:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.5.2.2.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:1:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:67:\"https://ps.w.org/contact-form-7/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=1176454\";s:7:\"caption\";s:16:\"screenshot-1.png\";}}s:4:\"tags\";a:5:{s:7:\"contact\";s:7:\"contact\";s:12:\"contact-form\";s:12:\"contact form\";s:5:\"email\";s:5:\"email\";s:8:\"feedback\";s:8:\"feedback\";s:4:\"form\";s:4:\"form\";}s:8:\"versions\";a:145:{s:3:\"1.1\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.1.zip\";s:4:\"1.10\";s:62:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.10.zip\";s:8:\"1.10.0.1\";s:66:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.10.0.1.zip\";s:6:\"1.10.1\";s:64:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.10.1.zip\";s:3:\"1.2\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.2.zip\";s:3:\"1.3\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.3.zip\";s:5:\"1.3.1\";s:63:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.3.1.zip\";s:5:\"1.3.2\";s:63:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.3.2.zip\";s:3:\"1.4\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.4.zip\";s:5:\"1.4.1\";s:63:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.4.1.zip\";s:5:\"1.4.2\";s:63:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.4.2.zip\";s:5:\"1.4.3\";s:63:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.4.3.zip\";s:5:\"1.4.4\";s:63:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.4.4.zip\";s:3:\"1.5\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.5.zip\";s:3:\"1.6\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.6.zip\";s:5:\"1.6.1\";s:63:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/contact-form-7.1.6.1.zip\";s:3:\"1.7\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.o